{"tid":1610290,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如何拆黨鐵","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T00:15:40.000Z","uid":273617,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1fdf795939b04ae4735f139451013a99c3fe22b5","tid":1610290,"uid":273617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"你地以為拆出閘機同售票機同跳閘有用咩？cmon James... 港共泵番幾十球就係番哂度，而且仲可以繼續運兵<br />\n<br />\n之前有巴打講過，一個站嘅核心其實係火牛房，有正副兩組牛，一爛哂兩個牛成個站會完全廢哂，車都冇辦法開<br />\n<br />\n至於點整爛，大家發揮創意啦，入火牛房要爆鋼門，要考慮埋呢點"},{"pid":"dbadecbe844fd76334f7f052ceced67efd9ad44b","tid":1610290,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:10:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警世：全世界唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵<br />\n俾啲骨氣啦唔該<br />\n呢頭出賣完香港人<br />\n轉個頭又不停俾錢佢哋賺<br />\n呢頭話要杯葛吉野家喜茶元氣<br />\n轉個頭又死去幫襯<br />\n我喺佢哋都笑鳩你哋班香港人<br />\n記住我哋先係Boss</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RhH6RYr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhH6RYr.jpg&h=bcfec53f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eyu1FRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feyu1FRM.jpg&h=483488e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"931cb48bb2a14e25213a5e51de4130322edd1a34","tid":1610290,"uid":183612,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5217be7bbc683d5ae1963c0aa12ca799d1b32f","tid":1610290,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be0f88a00d8f213b4c258146d8131c1743fe896","tid":1610290,"uid":148125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"931cb48bb2a14e25213a5e51de4130322edd1a34","tid":1610290,"uid":183612,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces